name: New Hubble image of NGC 2174
description:
The NASA/ESA Hubble Space Telescope has released this beautiful new image of part of NGC 2174, also known as the Monkey Head Nebula.

Name:	NGC 2174
Type:	Milky Way : Nebula : Appearance : Emission : H II Region
Distance:	6500 light years
Constellation:	Orion
Category:	Anniversary Nebulae

3,629 editions for the known 3,629 planetary systems to date.
